This is a Social Website Called Rails Social

To start this application make sure you have the correct version of Ruby.
In the terminal type in which ruby, if the following doesn't show up in your path you're
not using the correct version.   2.0.0-p481

If you don't have the correct version in the terminal type in
rvm use 2.0.0-p481

If you don't have rvm installed you can download it here:
https://rvm.io/rvm/install
and then run rvm use 2.0.0-p481 in your terminal

Good sites that explain what purpose the Gemfile.lock has and does
http://bundler.io/v1.3/rationale.html
https://richonrails.com/articles/how-does-the-gemfile-lock-file-work

